definitions.definition: A state in northwestern India , created in 1949 and replacing the former province of Rajputana . Capital: Jaipur .
Various parts of northwestern India within Rajputana province.

main_definition: A state in northwestern India , created in 1949 and replacing the former province of Rajputana . Capital: Jaipur . [from 20th c.]
